Description.SourceString: Callahan-class Battleships are massive, fully featured mobile bases. They pack enough firepower to devastate enemy naval vessels and their crew, or rain death on nearby shorelines while shrugging off punishment with its reinforced hull. Named for Caoiva’s founder and first Archon, who famously held fast in conflict with rival clans who wanted his head. Several Callahans remain anchored at Whedon’s Row Harbour.
